description_blz.en_US:
Rising Sun Kick now kicks up a Gust of Mist to heal 2 allies within 40 yds for 5. 

Spinning Crane Kick and Blackout Kick have a chance to kick up a Gust of Mist to heal 1 ally within 40 yds for 5.

Ahora, Patada del sol naciente genera una Racha de niebla que sana 5 p. de salud a 2 aliados en un radio de 40 m.
